00:08:25.185 --> 00:08:27.251
 and obesity-related diseases, 

00:08:27.251 --> 00:08:28.781
 at least in most people? 

00:08:28.781 --> 00:08:31.781
 What if being obese is just a metabolic response 

00:08:31.781 --> 00:08:34.002
 to something much more threatening, 

00:08:34.002 --> 00:08:36.213
 a hidden epidemic, 

00:08:36.213 --> 00:08:38.770
 what should we worry about the most? 

