00:08:57.039 --> 00:09:00.106
 and by the way, they are thought to be at greater risk for 

00:09:00.106 --> 00:09:02.261
 those metabolic diseases I mentioned above, 

00:09:02.261 --> 00:09:04.083
 in contrast to the group of obese. 

00:09:04.083 --> 00:09:06.320
 I don't know why, but maybe it comes as a result of that fact 

00:09:06.320 --> 00:09:09.010
 in their case, the cells have not yet understood it 

00:09:09.010 --> 00:09:12.295
 what to do with excess energy. 

00:09:12.295 --> 00:09:15.614
 So if a person may be obese and may not have insulin resistance, 

00:09:15.614 --> 00:09:17.485
 or he may be weak and have it, 

00:09:17.485 --> 00:09:21.918
 this indicates that obesity may be a camouflage 

00:09:21.918 --> 00:09:24.942
 for what is happening. 

00:09:24.942 --> 00:09:27.357
 So, if we were fighting a wrong war, 

00:09:27.357 --> 00:09:31.157
 to fight obesity instead of insulin resistance? 

00:09:31.157 --> 00:09:34.400
 Even worse, like blaming obese people 

00:09:34.400 --> 00:09:37.125
 does that mean we are blaming the victims? 

00:09:37.125 --> 00:09:40.844
 What if some of our core ideas about obesity 

00:09:40.844 --> 00:09:42.702
 are they wrong 

