00:13:05.447 --> 00:13:08.456
 And finally, when we identify it 

00:13:08.456 --> 00:13:11.484
 what are the safe and practical changes that people can make to their diet, 

00:13:11.484 --> 00:13:15.159
 how can we direct their behavior in that direction 

00:13:15.159 --> 00:13:17.412
 to become everyday 

