00:13:45.974 --> 00:13:48.253
 Most of them actually want to do the right gene, 

00:13:48.253 --> 00:13:51.622
 but they need to know what that is, 

00:13:51.622 --> 00:13:54.668
 and should work. 

00:13:54.668 --> 00:13:59.364
 I dream of the day when our patients 

00:13:59.364 --> 00:14:01.099
 will be able to weaken 

00:14:01.099 --> 00:14:03.912
 and cure themselves from insulin resistance, 

00:14:03.912 --> 00:14:06.642
 as a medical professional, 

00:14:06.642 --> 00:14:08.612
 we have sweated our mental baggage 

00:14:08.612 --> 00:14:11.938
 and we have healed ourselves from resisting ideas enough 

00:14:11.938 --> 00:14:15.028
 to return to our ideals of origin: 

00:14:15.028 --> 00:14:19.445
 open mind, with the courage to throw away yesterday's ideas 

00:14:19.445 --> 00:14:22.773
 when they do not yield results, 

00:14:22.773 --> 00:14:25.892
 and understanding that scientific truth is not the last word, 

00:14:25.892 --> 00:14:28.640
 but in constant evolution. 

00:14:28.640 --> 00:14:31.932
 Staying true to that path will be better for our patients 

00:14:31.932 --> 00:14:35.180
 and better for science, 

00:14:35.180 --> 00:14:38.174
 If obesity is nothing but camouflage 

00:14:38.174 --> 00:14:40.100
 of metabolic diseases, 

00:14:40.100 --> 00:14:45.397
 What good is it for us to punish those who suffer from it? 

00:14:45.397 --> 00:14:49.941
 It happens to me to think about the night in the emergency room 

00:14:49.941 --> 00:14:52.254
 7 years ago. 

00:14:52.254 --> 00:14:55.878
 I wish I could talk to that woman again. 

00:14:55.878 --> 00:14:59.133
 I would like to tell you how bad it was for me. 

00:14:59.133 --> 00:15:02.020
 I would tell her that as a doctor, I gave it to her 

00:15:02.020 --> 00:15:05.680
 the best clinical service I could, 

00:15:05.680 --> 00:15:09.577
 but as human beings, 

00:15:09.577 --> 00:15:11.985
 I didnâ€™t handle it properly. 

00:15:11.985 --> 00:15:16.230
 You didn't need my judgment. 

00:15:16.230 --> 00:15:20.728
 You needed my sympathy and regret, 

00:15:20.728 --> 00:15:22.723
 and most of all you needed a doctor 

00:15:22.723 --> 00:15:25.352
 who would be willing to consider 

00:15:25.352 --> 00:15:28.416
 the fact that you could be outside the framework of the system. 

00:15:28.416 --> 00:15:31.634
 Maybe the system, of which I was a part, 

00:15:31.634 --> 00:15:34.073
 did not help you. 

00:15:34.073 --> 00:15:36.874
 If you are watching this now, 

00:15:36.874 --> 00:15:41.112
 I hope you can forgive me. 

00:15:41.112 --> 00:15:45.112
 (Applause) 

